{"tid":289474,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無興趣討論一條假設題","createTime":"2017-06-19T04:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T18:17:48.000Z","uid":21837,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc5d580d32f5843bf2e5365152a6d9cb4c4c0e4","tid":289474,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"呢條假設題主要想試驗下大家會唔會為左舒適理想嘅居住環境同世界各地嘅美食而放棄自由同尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設有一個人，佢有能力提供一間獨立屋俾你住，包你係入面住要食嘅N餐，但你要答應佢去獨立屋時「探你」嘅一切要求，例如佢要求同你發生性行為你唔可以拒絕，又例如佢痾完屎要你幫佢抆你都唔可以拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話明係「探你」，呢個人唔會同你一齊住，只會間唔中上唻搵你，實際上成間屋都係你住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇，究竟佢offer嘅條件有咩咁吸引呢？<br />\n呢間獨立屋所有嘅設施都完整齊備，例如室內泳池，圖書室，影音院，打機房with高級電腦配置同N種遊戲器材，總之包羅萬有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要求新增嘅設備佢都會幫你搞<br />\n<br />\n同埋你想食啲咩美食，呢個人都有能力搵到專門人才整俾你食。例如你想食六星級法國大餐，佢會搵到幾個身價超高嘅大廚煮俾你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得，享受得呢啲，你要答應呢個人提出嘅所有要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後一樣想講嘅係，呢個人提出嘅要求唔會係刻意傷害你身體同生命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> DEAL<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> NOT DEAL"},{"pid":"cbe0ff05f0cbd0240c6be0e8d85cdb6845b03d5f","tid":289474,"uid":21837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"順帶一提，第一次嘅合約期為三年，簽左就呢三年都唔可以離開間獨立屋一步，如果離開同拒絕呢個人提出嘅要求就視為毀約，後果會係點請自行FF <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61286d204d693409197f1c225ef73b3fb5c337ca","tid":289474,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d17e2af55e58ce3b67f4c6a1c65227bb2ec2a26","tid":289474,"uid":123170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"朋友，屋企人入唔入得黎先"},{"pid":"8e0c8fb575bdb71a6688b533f737b6c277429bf4","tid":289474,"uid":38253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"plot twist: 樓主比闊太/有錢gay佬包養, 上連登問點算"},{"pid":"12cc3f3b22c4b92d06b17d828d9ba66314bcb317","tid":289474,"uid":65847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"平時出門口淨係為咗返工，冇自由又有點所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6c3eed1dd33824880d6e1e4221a0ad390b2065","tid":289474,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友，屋企人入唔入得黎先</blockquote><br />\n入得，但呢三年內同你一樣無得離開間屋，同埋簽約前要事先申請邊個跟你住，佢地係唔可以自由出入間屋，但滿足「嗰個人」嘅要求淨係你一個就得<br />\n<br />\n舉個例：你想同你女友一齊唻住呢間屋，但你同佢都唔可以係三年內離開呢間屋半步，假如「嗰個人」要你扮狗叫，淨係你扮就得，你女朋友唔洗。如果你申請左同女友住，屋企人係呢三年都唔可以入屋探你"},{"pid":"0dc926dafe134b1bb69f5711773d3c3868c488bf","tid":289474,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:39:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f86e74a5b366ee2def57bf8b39e77f4062cb6cf","tid":289474,"uid":24519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e66a3678eb2ea2685c2f5e618b746e7a96d7c3","tid":289474,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"我花盡畢生精力諗嘅假設題竟然無人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6c2faeecca97bc56649910146b7eab358b0e16","tid":289474,"uid":84089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"揭尾故feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da30394240c98b6b07b388ac0aa40a288aa5ab60","tid":289474,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0